item.description:
@KdotJinxx wrote:

[quote=“The Outsider, post:2, topic:424695”]I have a TV too. Nothing good on though. You have 100 errors because of a simple parenthesis error. Go back to what you just edited and find the extra bracket you have added.

What is the point in that spam poll? It’s just stupid and makes you look like a clown.[/quote]

What this obnoxious ‘clown’ was trying to say is somewhere you’ve added or removed one or more ‘{’ (brackets). Use an IDE such as eclipse to help you point this out if you cannot find it on your own.
